Parser in C for Even Number of A's

The C file - parser.c is a parser to check whether a given string could be parsed by the grammar:
S -> aSa | aa
(Even number of a's)
Input : Number of a's (We do not require the string as the character set of the language is limited to a only)
Output :  1) A step by step display of the parse tree
          2) A message indicating if the given number of a's can be parsed or not
Implementation : The given parser.c includes detailed comments of the same
